    "body": "I can't scroll down when I click \"Add Attachment\" in landscape mode. There is no scrollbar for the menu while some options are not displayed.\r\nPlus, when I open the menu then rotate the screen, the menu will disappear.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nScroll up and down like version 5.3.1.\r\nMenu does not disappear when switching between portrait and landscape modes.\r\nScreenshots from 5.3.1 with a scrollbar:\r\n![F549E9C3582EC424F70010B4319EF7CF](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/53887881/187010385-77ebfb56-57ad-4d81-b321-0cd9792da229.jpg)\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/53887881/187011180-2435065e-a9ff-4b47-a268-a68550c5da4b.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\nYou can't scroll downwards and the menu will disappear when you rotate the screen.\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/53887881/187011188-ee8dc27c-232b-4dc7-af7f-adbb39ad25cf.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Open a note in portrait mode.\r\n2. Click \"Add Attachment\".\r\n3. Switch to landscape mode and see the menu disappeared.\r\n4. Click \"Add Attachment\" in landscape mode.\r\n5. See the menu broken.\r\n\r\n### Environment\r\nOmninotes Version: 6.1.0\r\nGoogle Pixel 2 Android Version 8",
